    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for relative hemolysis index across the CPB operating envelope. Validation against the FDA benchmark dataset, combined with demonstrated mesh convergence and iterative solver convergence, supports the conclusion that the model is fit for the intended regulatory use. The credibility assessment team accepts the model for submission.",
